---
title: Portuguese-Style Chicken with Potato Wedges & Garden Salad
description: Brighten up your night with the vibrant paprika marinade on this tasty and tender Portuguese chicken. Infused with smokey flavours, plus sides of hearty potato wedges and a refreshing salad, this colourful plate adds a little international flair to the old meat-and-three!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/portuguese-chicken-golden-potatoes-2066cb05.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/portuguese-chicken-golden-potatoes-5b725f3bae08b5089224d8d2-726fed07.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 2480 kcal
  fat: 26.6 g
  saturated fat: 4.7 g
